@page "/"
@layout MainLayout

<h1>Welcome to CosmoBlazorSample</h1>

<p>This is a high-performance SSR-only Razor Components sample using CosmoApiServer.</p>

<div class="alert alert-info">
    Current Time: @DateTime.Now.ToLongTimeString()
</div>

<p>
    Features demonstrated:
    <ul>
        <li><b>Zero-Allocation Rendering:</b> Uses <code>IBufferWriter&lt;byte&gt;</code> for the hot-path.</li>
        <li><b>Layout Support:</b> <code>MainLayout.razor</code> is applied to all pages.</li>
        <li><b>Dependency Injection:</b> Services are shared across components.</li>
        <li><b>Form Validation:</b> Native <code>EditForm</code> support.</li>
    </ul>
</p>

<p>Check out the sidebar to explore more features!</p>
